Hayleys up 2 . 7 pct on foreign buying . Hayleys Ltd rose five rupees , or 2 . 7 percent , to 190 rupees on foreign buying of 3 , 100 shares in early Tuesday trading , dealers said . " Foreign buyers believe the share is cheap at current prices , because when the market peaked in early 1994 this share went to nearly 300 rupees , " said a local broker . Hayleys is a holding company for one of the three biggest conglomerates listed in Colombo . - - Colombo newsroom ( 941 ) 434319 
